{"tid":1182012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來之前無申有地俾人拉左個黑警後日就結案陳詞","createTime":"2019-06-02T00:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T01:27:44.000Z","uid":53568,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"91c3d827fb5396a4ab4af5658eb5fa74cd7f5d22","tid":1182012,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T00:58:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/article/男警就學期間瞞擁12幅地皮%E3%80%80涉呃學資處19萬元-B8WKV6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Farticle%2F%E7%94%B7%E8%AD%A6%E5%B0%B1%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%9F%E9%96%93%E7%9E%9E%E6%93%8112%E5%B9%85%E5%9C%B0%E7%9A%AE%25E3%2580%2580%E6%B6%89%E5%91%83%E5%AD%B8%E8%B3%87%E8%99%9519%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-B8WKV6&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJIwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=4eaa90f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/article/男警就學期間瞞擁12幅地皮%E3%80%80涉呃學資處19萬元-B8WKV6</a><br />\n<br />\n涉案被告古俊輝被控於2013年9月至2014年3月間，及2014年5月至12月間，詐騙學資處根據專上學生資助計劃，分別向他發放約9.39萬港元及約9.94萬港元。被告於案發時就讀香港專業教育學院的銀行及金融高級文憑課程，他於2017年4月已將涉案資助金全數歸還政府。<br />\n<br />\n有咁多地都仲呃政府錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd362cc596d0f38720c62f98e72d8c114da971ce","tid":1182012,"uid":189109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T01:04:35.000Z","msg":"咁有錢點解唔去做蝙蝠俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38850ab695271feac2f527c1411c117475183ae1","tid":1182012,"uid":108016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T01:25:24.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"ed4c9d8fe7d593b2fa4f2f487d633b74f177c351","tid":1182012,"uid":133988,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T01:30:49.000Z","msg":"應該立法啦<br />\n紀律部隊犯罪應該立即死刑<br />\n紀律部隊知法犯法 罪加一等<br />\n覺得自己唔會犯法咪去做"},{"pid":"b10fc8ddd7e1913a9da8866081ccc340e69dc9c5","tid":1182012,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed4c9d8fe7d593